Class MagneticFlux

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.external.navigation.MagneticFlux

  • public class MagneticFlux
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of MagneticFlux represent a three-dimensional magnetic strength vector. Units are in tesla (NOT microtesla).
    See Also:
    https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tesla_(unit)
